parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes to respond promptly in wet driving conditions can lead to increased stopping distances, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes take several seconds to respond when applied in wet conditions
requiring pumping of the brake pedal to slow the vehicle
or the brakes fail to stop the car initially
only to respond after a delay.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition coil can cause the engine to run poorly, leading to a loss of power, misfires, and potentially stalling, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially when driving on the freeway.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
and the O2 sensors are damaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure due to Cylinder Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of one or more cylinders can cause the engine to stall or seize, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Rattling sound from the engine bay
change in tone and/or pitch when the clutch is engaged/disengaged
engine stalling or dying without warning

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Inadequate Repair by Dealership
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dealership to properly diagnose and repair the issue can lead to further engine damage, increased repair costs, and prolonged downtime, causing inconvenience and frustration to the vehicle owner.
symptoms: Dealership unable to diagnose or repair the issue
lack of transparency or communication from the dealership
and inconsistent or changing repair recommendations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause the vehicle to grind or hesitate when shifting gears, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stalling, which can result in injury or damage.
The failure of the rear axle or differential can cause loss of control, accidents, or stalling, which can result in injury or damage.
symptoms: distinct metallic sound coming from the rear end of the vehicle.
